e taxonomy.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Q1\",\"Q2\",\"Q3\",\"Q4\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Q1 partly\",\"Q2 partly\",\"Q3 partly\",\"Q4 partly\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Add a preset palette/font/layout chooser to sk-interface-design\",\"reason\":\"Lovable's curated questions are useful as a contrast pattern but would weaken the anti-default mandate if copied as presets\",\"evidence\":\"https://docs.lovable.dev/features/design-guidance.md\"}],\"durationMs\":620000,\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-14T09:30:00Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55fast-1781420686076-jgor8g\",\"generation\":1,\"sources\":[\"https://docs.lovable.dev/features/design-guidance.md\",\"https://docs.lovable.dev/features/preview-toolbar.md\",\"https://docs.lovable.dev/features/browser-testing.md\",\"https://docs.lovable.dev/features/design-systems.md\",\"https://docs.lovable.dev/features/knowledge.md\",\"https://docs.lovable.dev/features/skills.md\"]}\n6: {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"run\":3,\"iteration\":3,\"mode\":\"research\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Figma Make: plan mode, Make kits, guidelines, local-codebase editing, and design round-tripping\",\"findingsCount\":7,\"newInfoRatio\":0.72,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Figma Make overlaps on context and visual feedback but adds reviewable plan.md, guidelines-as-context, Make kits, local commit/PR semantics, and copy-preview-as-layers round trip.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Q1\",\"Q2\",\"Q3\",\"Q4\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Q1 partly\",\"Q2 partly\",\"Q3 partly\",\"Q4 partly\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Replicate Figma Make local repository branch/PR management inside mcp-magicpath\",\"reason\":\"Git branching and PR creation belong to sk-git/system workflows, not the MagicPath CLI skill\",\"evidence\":\"https://help.figma.com/hc/en-us/articles/40775535020695-Make-in-your-local-codebase\"}],\"durationMs\":640000,\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-14T09:35:00Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55fast-1781420686076-jgor8g\",\"generation\":1,\"sources\":[\"https://help.figma.com/hc/en-us/articles/31304412302231-Explore-Figma-Make\",\"https://help.figma.com/hc/en-us/articles/40830441709719-Use-plan-mode-in-Figma-Make\",\"https://help.figma.com/hc/en-us/articles/39241689698839-Get-started-with-Make-kits\",\"https://help.figma.com/hc/en-us/articles/35946832653975-Use-your-design-system-package-in-Make-kits\",\"https://help.figma.com/hc/en-us/articles/33665861260823-Add-guidelines-to-Figma-Make\",\"https://help.figma.com/hc/en-us/articles/40775535020695-Make-in-your-local-codebase\"]}\n7: {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"run\":4,\"iteration\":4,\"mode\":\"research\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Subframe and adjacent design-to-code tools: deterministic presentational code, sync boundaries, MCP design access\",\"findingsCount\":6,\"newInfoRatio\":0.58,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Subframe adds a clean separable model: deterministic presentational UI, one-way synced design-system components, wrapper-owned business logic, and MCP-accessible design documents.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Q1\",\"Q2\",\"Q3\",\"Q4\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Q1 partly\",\"Q2 partly\",\"Q3 partly\",\"Q4\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Make generated MagicPath component source a two-way design-system source of truth\",\"reason\":\"Subframe itself treats component sync as one-way and warns local edits are overwritten; mcp-magicpath should keep generated files and app wrappers distinct\",\"evidence\":\"https://docs.subframe.com/concepts/syncing-components.md\"}],\"durationMs\":590000,\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-14T09:40:00Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55fast-1781420686076-jgor8g\",\"generation\":1,\"sources\":[\"https://docs.subframe.com/overview.md\",\"https://docs.subframe.com/concepts/code-generation.md\",\"https://docs.subframe.com/concepts/design-to-code.md\",\"https://docs.subframe.com/concepts/syncing-components.md\",\"https://docs.subframe.com/learn/ask-ai/prompt-to-design.md\",\"https://docs.subframe.com/learn/ask-ai/making-quick-edits.md\",\"https://docs.subframe.com/g