search/research/lineages/gpt55fast\",\"reason\":\"config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir override supplied by operator; resolveArtifactRoot command intentionally not run\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-14T09:20:01Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55fast-1781420686076-jgor8g\",\"generation\":1}\n{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"spec_synthesis_deferred\",\"mode\":\"research\",\"reason\":\"operator constrained this fan-out lineage to write only inside artifact_dir; parent spec.md pre-init and post-synthesis write-back were skipped\",\"generatedFence\":\"deep-research/spec-findings\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-14T09:20:02Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55fast-1781420686076-jgor8g\",\"generation\":1}\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"run\":1,\"iteration\":1,\"mode\":\"research\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"v0 by Vercel: live visual editing, registries, and Figma import\",\"findingsCount\":6,\"newInfoRatio\":1.0,\"noveltyJustification\":\"First evidence pass; v0 adds live-preview visual controls, Tailwind-aware pending edits, Figma token extraction, and registry context beyond packet 005's Claude Design baseline.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Q1\",\"Q2\",\"Q3\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Q1 partly\",\"Q2 partly\",\"Q3 partly\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Clone v0 end-to-end deployment and backend agent\",\"reason\":\"Platform hosting and full-stack deployment exceed two CLI-skill scope\",\"evidence\":\"https://vercel.com/docs/v0\"}],\"durationMs\":600000,\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-14T09:25:00Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55fast-1781420686076-jgor8g\",\"generation\":1,\"sources\":[\"https://vercel.com/docs/v0\",\"https://vercel.com/docs/v0/design-mode\",\"https://vercel.com/docs/v0/design-systems\",\"https://vercel.com/docs/v0/figma\"]}\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"run\":2,\"iteration\":2,\"mode\":\"research\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Lovable: pre-build design guidance, preview-toolbar feedback, design-system adherence, and browser testing\",\"findingsCount\":7,\"newInfoRatio\":0.82,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Lovable confirms a distinct pre-build three-direction gate and an explicit design-system violation scanner; overlaps with 005 fidelity loops but adds a sharper governance taxonomy.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Q1\",\"Q2\",\"Q3\",\"Q4\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Q1 partly\",\"Q2 partly\",\"Q3 partly\",\"Q4 partly\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Add a preset palette/font/layout chooser to sk-interface-design\",\"reason\":\"Lovable's curated questions are useful as a contrast pattern but would weaken the anti-default mandate if copied as presets\",\"evidence\":\"https://docs.lovable.dev/features/design-guidance.md\"}],\"durationMs\":620000,\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-14T09:30:00Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55fast-1781420686076-jgor8g\",\"generation\":1,\"sources\":[\"https://docs.lovable.dev/features/design-guidance.md\",\"https://docs.lovable.dev/features/preview-toolbar.md\",\"https://docs.lovable.dev/features/browser-testing.md\",\"https://docs.lovable.dev/features/design-systems.md\",\"https://docs.lovable.dev/features/knowledge.md\",\"https://docs.lovable.dev/features/skills.md\"]}\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"run\":3,\"iteration\":3,\"mode\":\"research\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Figma Make: plan mode, Make kits, guidelines, local-codebase editing, and design round-tripping\",\"findingsCount\":7,\"newInfoRatio\":0.72,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Figma Make overlaps on context and visual feedback but adds reviewable plan.md, guidelines-as-context, Make kits, local commit/PR semantics, and copy-preview-as-layers round trip.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Q1\",\"Q2\",\"Q3\",\"Q4\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Q1 partly\",\"Q2 partly\",\"Q3 partly\",\"Q4 partly\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Replicate Figma Make local repository branch/PR management inside mcp-magicpath\",\"reason\":\"Git branching and PR creation belong to sk-git/system workflows, not the MagicPath CLI skill\",\"evidence\":\"https://help.figma.com/hc/en-us/articles/40775535020695-Make-in-your-local-codebase\"}],\"durationMs\":640000,\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-14T09:35:00Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55fast-1781420686076-jgor8g\",\"generation\":1,\"sources\":[\"https://help.figma.com/hc/en-us/articles/31304412302231-Explore-Figma-Make\",\"https://help.figma.com/hc/en-us/articles/40830441709719-Use-plan-mode-in-Figma-Make\",\"https://help.figma.com/hc/en-us/articles/39241689698839-Get-started-with-Make-kits\",\"https://help.figma.com/hc/en-us/articles/35946832653975-Use-your-design-system-package-in-Make-kits\",\"https://help.figma.com/hc/en-us/articles/33665861260823-Add-guidelines-to-Figma-Make\",\"https://help.figma.com/hc/en-us/articles/40775535020695-Make-in-your-local-codebase\"]}\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"run\":4,\"iteration\":4,\"mode\":\"research\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Subframe and adjacent design-to-code tools: deterministic presentational code, sync boundaries, MCP design access\",\"findingsCount\":6,\"newInfoRatio\":0.58,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Subframe adds a clean separable model: deterministic presentational UI, one-way synced design-system components, wrapper-owned business logic, and MCP-accessible design documents.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Q1\",\"Q2\",\"Q3\",\"Q4\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Q1 partly\",\"Q2 partly\",\"Q3 partly\",\"Q4\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Make generated MagicPath component source a two-way design-system source of truth\",\"reason\":\"Subframe itself treats component sync as one-way and warns local edits are overwritten; mcp-magicpath should keep generated files and app wrappers distinct\",\"evidence\":\"https://docs.subframe.com/concepts/syncing-components.md\"}],\"durationMs\":590000,\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-14T09:40:00Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55fast-1781420686076-jgor8g\",\"generation\":1,\"sources\":[\"https://docs.subframe.com/overview.md\",\"https://docs.subframe.com/concepts/code-generation.md\",\"https://docs.subframe.com/concepts/design-to-code.md\",\"https://docs.subframe.com/concepts/syncing-components.md\",\"https://docs.subframe.com/learn/ask-ai/prompt-to-design.md\",\"https://docs.subframe.com/learn/ask-ai/making-quick-edits.md\",\"https://docs.subframe.com/guides/mcp-server.md\",\"https://docs.animaapp.com/docs/getting-started\",\"https://www.builder.io/c/docs/import-from-figma\"]}\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"run\":5,\"iteration\":5,\"mode\":\"research\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Deduplication against packet 005 and prioritized adoption matrix for both local skills\",\"findingsCount\":8,\"newInfoRatio\":0.31,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Mostly synthesis and dedupe, but it produced new prioritized patterns: direction-gate, element-target grammar, adherence scanner, plan artifact, and presentational wrapper boundary.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Q1\",\"Q2\",\"Q3\",\"Q4\",\"Q5\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Q1\",\"Q2\",\"Q3\",\"Q4\",\"Q5\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Hosted web-product capabilities: live multiplayer canvas, publishing/hosting, billing, enterprise admin, app backend setup\",\"reason\":\"Out of scope for lean CLI skills; preserve as negative knowledge rather than recommendations\",\"evidence\":\"https://docs.lovable.dev/introduction/welcome.md\"},{\"approach\":\"Subtle visual-diff automation as a completion gate\",\"reason\":\"Lovable documents browser testing as unreliable for subtle visual design details; use human/design judgment plus screenshots instead\",\"evidence\":\"https://docs.lovable.dev/features/browser-testing.md\"}],\"durationMs\":540000,\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-14T09:45:00Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55fast-1781420686076-jgor8g\",\"generation\":1,\"sources\":[\"file:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/005-claude-design-parity-research/research/research.md\",\"file:.opencode/skills/sk-interface-design/SKILL.md\",\"file:.opencode/skills/mcp-magicpath/SKILL.md\"]}\n{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"synthesis_complete\",\"mode\":\"research\",\"totalIterations\":5,\"answeredCount\":5,\"tot