{"type":"text","timestamp":1782532863257,"sessionID":"ses_0f8ce9c97ffeoYuqUQ1KEMV7ea","part":{"id":"prt_f073cefa2001ouKderFW414GYt","messageID":"msg_f073c992d001IwpgMZzz4qF3jT","sessionID":"ses_0f8ce9c97ffeoYuqUQ1KEMV7ea","type":"text","text":"Two concrete routing defects emerged from the evidence: the pseudocode keyword loop is not executable as written, and the `../shared/register.md` \"ALWAYS\" load is not represented in the parseable resource map or router replay output. I’m treating these as top-priority research findings, not editing the live skill.","time":{"start":1782532861858,"end":1782532863255},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0b6eb2168d3117a8016a3f4afdda948191b8bdd1f49fc5a450","phase":"commentary"}}}}
